OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Ffading to leave a mostly dry night
OL,7,Fwith variable cloud. Turning locally
OL,8,Fchilly, with some patchy fog and rural
OL,9,Ffrost forming. Cloud increasing from
OL,10,Fthe south later, bringing some showery
OL,11,Frain to the west towards daybreak.
OL,12,FLight winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FA cloudy start in places with
OL,15,Fshowers. Cloud breaking to give bright
OL,16,For sunny spells into the afternoon but
OL,17,Fwith locally heavy showers in the
OL,18,Fnorth. Feeling warm in sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
