OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FSaturday, mostly dry with warm bright
OL,7,Fspells. Chance of showers moving from
OL,8,Fsouth later and into Sunday. Becoming
OL,9,Fbreezy and noticeably cooler. A few
OL,10,Fshowers Monday, breezy and feeling
OL,11,Fcool.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
